FBIS3-55119 "drsov004_f_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 National Affairs Poll Indicates Kuchma More Popular Than Kravchuk LD0501190494 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 1200 GMT 5 Jan 94 LD0501190494 Kiev UNIAR Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] Kiev, 5 Jan -- At the end of December 1993, experts from the joint venture Socio-Gallup conducted an opinion poll in every region of the republic, which resulted in the rating of the popularity of politicians on the five-point scale being as follows: ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Leonid Kuchma |2.11 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Leonid Kravchuk |2.07 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Vyacheslav Chornovil |1.61 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Ivan Plyushch |1.56 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Ihor Yuhnovskyy |1.50 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Volodymyr Yavorivskyy |1.42 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Volodymyr Hrynyov |1.22 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Kostyantyn Morozov |1.22 | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
